(98, 3, '2017-11-06 13:28:43', '2017-11-06 13:28:43', '<h2>Tender preparation, invites of bids and selection of contractor:</h2>\nAfter an approval of Plan of action and Budget Estimates we start complaining Tender documents for the repair work. A Tender is an important document which will inform the quality of the repair project. The details of work to be carried out as per the Technical specifications listed in the Tender to bind the Contractor to follow the same strictly.\n\nWe will prepare Tender Document on your behalf indicating all tasks to be achieved as part of the whole project together with all conditions of clauses relevant to completion of the same successfully.\n\n&nbsp;\n<h2>How to select a Contractor:</h2>\nThe final steps before start of the repair project is bid invites from contractor. We give the details of work of the project duly selected carefully and invite technically and financially a sound contractor to give their quotes for the same. All sealed Tenders will be opened in your presence and go ahead to prepare a comparison report based on detailed study of all quotes.\n\nAfter careful consideration and negotiation rounds a most suited contractor is selected to carry out the repair job.\n\n&nbsp;\n\nCharges\n\nCharges applicable as per your buildings\n\nBuilding Ground + 4 = 11,000/-\n\nBuilding Ground + 7 = 21,000/-', 'Method of working', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '89-autosave-v1', '', '', '2017-11-06 13:28:43', '2017-11-06 13:28:43', '', 89, 'http://paintrepairconsultant.com/2017/11/06/89-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
